---debrief form--
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>

    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="block" style>
            <div id="content">
                <h4>Thank you for your participation in this experiment.</h4>
                <p>
                    "Now your participation is completed. We will review some key points of experiment in the following. Our task aims to detect the kindss of individual beliefs in various macroeconomic and mutual fund patterns. "
                </p>
                <p>
                    "During the experiment, after learning macroeconomic-related and fund-specific information, you tried to guess the value of one mutual fund for 20 points with feedback and then predicted an additional 20 points without feedback. The data you saw may have come from another participant and your prediction may be used as training for a future participant. We will see how expectations evolve as they are passed down and test whether predictions differ depending on the provided information."
                </p>
                <p>
                    "Your participation is greatly appreciated by the researchers and the data collected could help better our understanding of various financial market patterns. If you require further information, please contact : lin.li.1@warwick.ac.uk. Thank you! "
                </p>
            </div>
            <div style class="row">
                <button style="float:right;">Next</button>
                :: after
            </div>
            <div style="height:10px;"></div>
        </div>
    </body>
